Configuration  Configure Nuxt Mongoose with the   mongoose  property.     export   default   defineNuxtConfig  ({
   mongoose: {
     uri:   'process.env.MONGODB_URI'  ,
     options: {},
     modelsDir:   'models'  ,
     devtools:   true  ,
   },
 })




































